text: Rio das Pedras is a municipality in the State of São Paulo, Brazil, located at the Microregion of Piracicaba. As of 2010, it has 29.508 people and an area of 226.657 square kilometers. ==Notable people== *Ivan Football player ==References== ==External links== *Official site Category:Municipalities in São Paulo (state)
